:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"拍多d笑片好過啦<br />\n好似愛回家，超時空男臣果d咁<br />\n嘻嘻哈哈又過左一個鐘<br />\n又低成本<br />\n<br />\n宮鬥劇朝早返工都睇到厭啦<br />\n夜晚仲要睇啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}